COMMENT ON COLUMN PRODUCT.THUMBNAIL IS '대표이미지';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PRODUCT.SALE IS '할인률';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PRODUCT.DELIVERY IS '배송비';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PRODUCT.COUNT IS '조회수';
